                Muranus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ala</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Flavia</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Androuri <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> civis <lb n="4"/>Secuanus <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXI <lb n="5"/>N
